Requirements:
Git
Titanium Studio (http://www.appcelerator.com/titanium/titanium-studio/)
Android SDK and/or iOS SDK

Installation:
1) Meet all requirements and have them installed
2) Clone this repository
3) Open Titanium Studio
4) File > Import
5) Hack & Run!

API Calls:
http://conference.phpbenelux.eu/2014/api/phpbenelux/crew/
http://conference.phpbenelux.eu/2014/api/phpbenelux/schedule/
http://conference.phpbenelux.eu/2014/api/phpbenelux/sponsors/
http://conference.phpbenelux.eu/2014/api/get_recent_posts/